{"tid":720170,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得鳴人嘅衣着喺成套火影都係柒嘅極致","createTime":"2018-06-27T17:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T21:08:55.000Z","uid":25612,"like":17,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c92b9e35ec39f79e2fb4b92d2765bcf0a9747f10","tid":720170,"uid":25612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T17:24:45.000Z","msg":"細細個着連身同色套裝比起其他人都算柒<br />\n丫屌你到左疾風傳大個左都仲係同一個style<br />\n<br />\n去到忍界大戰尾段件衫俾人打爛曬<br />\n上衣唔拉拉鏈7分袖叫好睇返少少<br />\n<br />\n都唔講永遠上唔到中忍着唔到嗰件中忍背心<br />\n轉換下啲合群嘅衣着<br />\n做左火影竟然唔係跟佢老豆着長袍<br />\n件披風短到連屎忽都遮唔到<br />\n個頭鏟到平頭咁款仲衰過後生嗰陣<br />\n<br />\n跟下佢老豆個style學下飛雷神不知食到幾多忍界囡囡啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18cba2474cffc21c854da559aa4cc029535b1d33","tid":720170,"uid":44391,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T17:30:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e6f504330e613ae1d6dd7ed215ea441f170c46d","tid":720170,"uid":52539,"like":75,"dislike":2,"score":73,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T17:34:05.000Z","msg":"如果唔整柒嗚人 佐助既意義係邊?"},{"pid":"4924923753a4ac1e94a5c657bd8327c68a718e26","tid":720170,"uid":111625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e6f504330e613ae1d6dd7ed215ea441f170c46d","tid":720170,"uid":52539,"like":75,"dislike":2,"score":73,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T17:34:05.000Z","msg":"如果唔整柒嗚人 佐助既意義係邊?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T17:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89ea49a8f284d5faded33d03cb1b32b0cac548a","tid":720170,"uid":85803,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4924923753a4ac1e94a5c657bd8327c68a718e26","tid":720170,"uid":111625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e6f504330e613ae1d6dd7ed215ea441f170c46d","tid":720170,"uid":52539,"like":75,"dislike":2,"score":73,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T17:34:0